<taxonomicName box="[320,469,1940,1962]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Silba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="519" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="boulangi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[320,469,1940,1962]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="519">Silba boulangi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[475,555,1941,1962]" pageId="4" pageNumber="519" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[475,555,1941,1962]" pageId="4" pageNumber="519">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
5. Phallus lateral view. 6. Same, ventral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,314,1970,1993]" pageId="4" pageNumber="519">FIGURES 7–8.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[320,444,1971,1993]" class="Insecta" family="Lonchaeidae" genus="Silba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="519" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bredoi" status="sp. nov.">
